encounters.summary:
{
  "narration": "In the dim, corrupted cave filled with glowing fungi and choking spores, Eirik Hearthwise and Scout Kira faced off against a vicious Corrupted Cave Fisher and two Tainted Stirges. The encounter began with a fierce assault as the Fisher lunged and the stirges attacked swiftly, one piercing Kira's shoulder. Eirik responded decisively by summoning a radiant Spiritual Weapon and striking first at the stirges, quickly destroying one and severely wounding the other. Despite Kira's valiant efforts with her bow, the corrupted creatures pressed their attack, landing a brutal claw strike against Eirik. With resilience and divine power, Eirik healed his wounds mid-combat and continued to press the assault, methodically eliminating the tainted stirges. Left alone and severely wounded, the Corrupted Cave Fisher became the final, desperate opponent. The battle crescendoed as Eirik's Spiritual Weapon and mace landed crushing blows, with Kira supporting from range. In a climactic strike, the Fisher was brought down, its corrupted form collapsing amidst the faint smell of decay. The cave fell silent, the dark taint lifted for now. Eirik and Kira stood victorious, bloodied but unbroken, in the heart of the corrupted domain.",
  "combat_round": 5,
  "actions": [
    "Round 1: Corrupted Cave Fisher missed Eirik with a claw attack; two Tainted Stirges attacked, one wounding Kira with a proboscis; Eirik summoned Spiritual Weapon and struck twice, killing one stirge and damaging the other; Kira's arrow missed.",
    "Round 2: Corrupted Cave Fisher claw attack missed; Tainted Stirges attacked but were repelled; Eirik struck the remaining stirge twice, further damaging it; Kira's arrow missed again.",
    "Round 3: Corrupted Cave Fisher landed a critical claw hit on Eirik; the last stirge attempted an attack but failed; Eirik destroyed the final stirge with mace and Spiritual Weapon attacks.",
    "Round 4: Corrupted Cave Fisher attacked fiercely, critically injuring Eirik; Eirik cast Cure Wounds, healing 13 HP, then hit the Fisher with Spiritual Weapon dealing radiant damage; Kira's arrow glanced off the Fisher's shell.",
    "Round 5: Eirik struck the Fisher with Spiritual Weapon and mace, dealing combined 17 damage, defeating it; Kira's final arrow missed but the Fisher collapsed, ending the combat.",
    "Post-Combat: Both Tainted Stirges and the Corrupted Cave Fisher lie dead on the cave floor, their corrupted bodies twitching no more."
  ],
  "experience_awarded": {
    "total_xp": 400,
    "participants": {
      "Eirik_Hearthwise": 200,
      "Scout_Kira": 200
    }
  }
}

{
  "narration": "In the eerie glow of the corrupted entry cave, Eirik Hearthwise and Scout Kira faced a fierce tainted stirge, a monstrous insect swollen with corruption and hunger. The battle began with Kira's swift arrow missing its target as the stirge dodged expertly. Eirik struck next, delivering a powerful mace blow that badly wounded the creature but failed to finish it. The stirge retaliated fiercely, latching onto Eirik with its venomous proboscis and draining his vitality. Despite the pain and the corrupted bite, Kira attempted another shot but was thwarted by the close proximity of the stirge. Finally, Eirik summoned his resolve and, with another critical strike, crushed the tainted stirge against the cave wall, ending its threat. The cave fell silent, the immediate danger quelled, and the party caught their breath amidst the sickly fungi glow. The defeated tainted stirge lay slumped, its corrupted body twitching no more.",
  "combat_round": 2,
  "actions": [
    {
      "creature": "Scout Kira",
      "action": "Fired a shortbow shot at the tainted stirge but missed due to the creature's evasive maneuvering."
    },
    {
      "creature": "Eirik Hearthwise",
      "action": "Made a critical mace attack roll (natural 20), dealing significant damage (6 + 5 + bonus) to the tainted stirge, reducing it from full health to near death."
    },
    {
      "creature": "Tainted Stirge",
      "action": "Attacked Eirik with a bite, successfully latching on and draining life, causing pain and potential necrotic effects."
    },
    {
      "creature": "Scout Kira",
      "action": "Attempted a second shortbow shot but missed due to the stirge's close proximity to Eirik."
    },
    {
      "creature": "Eirik Hearthwise",
      "action": "Delivered a finishing critical mace attack (natural 20) dealing 12 damage, destroying the tainted stirge completely."
    }
  ],
  "defeated_monsters": [
    {
      "name": "Tainted Stirge",
      "challenge_rating": 1,
      "xp": 200,
      "status": "dead",
      "description": "A corrupted insect-like creature with swollen body and venomous proboscis, defeated after two critical hits from Eirik."
    }
  ],
  "xp_awarded": {
    "total_xp": 200,
    "participants": 2,
    "xp_per_participant": 100,
    "participants_list": [
      "Eirik Hearthwise",
      "Scout Kira"
    ]
  }
}

